Si '''Masataka Kosaka''' (高坂 正堯 diad gendat ya Hapon) (Mayo 8, 1934 anggad Mayo 15, 1996), sakey ya eksperto ed international politics. Datin professor na [[Kyoto University]]. Enianak ed [[Baley na Kyoto]] ya kumadwan panguloan na laki nen [[Masaaki Kosaka]] ya sakey eksperto ed philosophy. Diad unibersidad, nanaral diad leksab nen [[Ryoichi Takaoka]] san [[Masamichi Inoki]]. Onong ed Inoki, si Masataka Kosaka so sankanayarian ya binangatan to.

